summary:
this might be an unpopular opinion but i have an issue with the fanon version of peter
first of all, i dont think hed put...
body:
this might be an unpopular opinion but i have an issue with the fanon version of peter

first of all, i dont think hed put “mr/ms” in front of everyone’s name. he says mr. stark, in my opinion, because

1) the guy is his boss.

2) he respects him.

3) the guys famous.

tbh i think the biggest point here is that tonys his boss. hell i call my boss ma'am and she hates it.

I don’t think hed say mr. loki. i dont think he’d say mr. hawkeye. hes a teenager. respectful? yes. the mentality of a five year old? no

that’s another thing. peter benjamin parker is a genius. that’s not an exaggeration. he’s super smart. please stop dumbing him down.

and books smart =/= common sense smarts, trust me, he can still be a genius who is naive as hell. in the mcu hes still new to hero-ing so it make sense that he doesnt always make the smartest choices.

speaking of him not being a five year old!! hes a teenager. hes allowed to swear. would he swear infront of adults? i dont really get that kind of vibe, probably not. would he swear with his friends? probably every once in a while! i dont think he has a trucker mouth but the kid is allowed to let out a, ‘shit’ without :0000 you said swear words!!!!!!

OPE! And flash!!!!! another thing, peter isnt made of glass! he can handle flash! even in the comics, he always felt he could handle flash. hes got thick skin i mean it might irk him but hes not going home crying every night digging into the tub of icecream and wallowing in self pity. i dont think he gets beat up behind dennys by flash and the gang at 2 o'clock sharp. i dont know the direction theyre going w/ flash in the mcu but i think its more… peters not upset by what flash says hes annoyed. like 'yeah okay jackass’. i also don’t think flash hates him because hes not rich (ive seen that before?) i think its more of a competition type of situation. where flash doesnt like that he has to try to be better than Peter, academically wise

things fanon didnt erase: his extreme selflessness and awkwardness. good job !

summary: - You're a good cop, dad. You wear this token and hold this gun, because you know, if not you, it will be someone else. The one...
body: • - You’re a good cop, dad. You wear this token and hold this gun, because you know, if not you, it will be someone else. The one who should not do this. I only wear this mask because … … because it frees me from responsibility. I thought I was special. And Peter Parker died because he was trying to follow my example. I have to take this responsibility. To make his death mean something. And I can’t do it in a prison cell. From now on, this mask is my sign. And if I don’t decide what it means … … then monsters will do it, like this one
